primary.request: Register for a new portal account
primary.context: Caller received a message saying their ownership type requires special handling for registration
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller's identity using contract ID and name, then sent a Clubhouse registration link via email.

steps: Caller requested help with website registration.
Agent attempted lookup via phone number (failed) and then contract ID (success).
Agent verified identity by asking for name and state of residence.
Agent confirmed contact details on file.
Agent sent registration link via email.
Caller confirmed this was all they needed.

clarifications.note: Agent clarifying if user needs registration or password reset
Agent asking for spelling of name

corrections.note: First name provided didn't match; caller provided parent's name

actions.detail: Lookup by Brazilian phone number failed
Verified name and state of residence
Sent Clubhouse registration link to email on file

insights.summary: The caller needed help registering for the new website after seeing a 'special handling' error. The agent successfully verified the account using a contract ID and sent the registration link via email.
insights.verbatim: Perfect. So I have to log in in Vacatia, the new website.
